item.title: 2019-04-16: Honeymoon Day1
item.description: The day before depature We decided to carry out our luggage by Sagawa Express to the Handea airport. The luggage was to be carried by the carrier the day before. Until the day I was very busy with packing. That day I could not sleep much because of excitement. The depature day, at the airport The plane we were to ride was at 11:35. We wanted to arrive at the airport two hours ago, so we left home at 7:30.
